BUILDFactoryCalcMaxAvailableAmountTest
├── when no deposits have been made
│   └── it should return zero
└── when a deposit has been made
    └── it should return the total deposited amount as max available
    └── when all tokens are withdrawn
    │   └── it should return zero as max available
    └── when tokens are allocated to a season
        └── it should return the correct max available
        └── when a refund has started
            └── it should return the correct max available
            └── when some tokens are withdrawn
                └── it should return the correct max available
